#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:2
msgid "权限"
msgstr "Privileges"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:5
msgid "UAC"
msgstr "UAC"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:8
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:9
msgid ""
"UAC (User Account Control) 是Windows Vista 和 Windows Server 2008 "
"引入的一个安全机制，当一些敏感操作发生时，会跳出提示显式要求系统权限。"
msgstr "UAC (User Account Control) is a security mechanism introduced in Windows Vista and Windows Server 2008. When certain sensitive operations occur, it displays a prompt that explicitly requests system privileges."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:11
msgid ""
"当用户登陆Windows时，每个用户都会被授予一个access token，这个token中有security identifier (SID) "
"的信息，决定了用户的权限。"
msgstr "When a user logs on to Windows, each user is granted an access token. This token contains security identifier (SID) information, which determines the user's privileges."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:14
msgid "会触发UAC的操作"
msgstr "Operations That Trigger UAC"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:15
msgid "以管理员权限启动应用"
msgstr "Launch applications as administrator"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:16
msgid "修改系统、UAC设置"
msgstr "Modify system or UAC settings"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:17
msgid "修改没有权限的文件或者目录（ %SystemRoot% / %ProgramFiles% 等 ）"
msgstr "Modify files or directories without permission, such as %SystemRoot% / %ProgramFiles%"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:18
msgid "修改ACL (access control list)"
msgstr "Modify ACL (access control list)"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:19
msgid "安装驱动"
msgstr "Install drivers"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:20
msgid "增删账户，修改账户类型，激活来宾账户"
msgstr "Add/delete accounts, modify account types, and enable the guest account"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:23
msgid "ByPass"
msgstr "Bypass"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:24
msgid "DLL相关"
msgstr "DLL-related techniques"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:25
msgid "进程注入"
msgstr "Process injection"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:26
msgid "注册表"
msgstr "Registry"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:29
msgid "权限提升"
msgstr "Privilege Escalation"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:30
msgid "权限提升有多重方式，有利用二进制漏洞、逻辑漏洞等技巧。利用二进制漏洞获取权限的方式是利用运行在内核态中的漏洞来执行代码。比如内核、驱动中的UAF或者其他类似的漏洞，以获得较高的权限。"
msgstr "There are multiple ways to perform privilege escalation, including techniques that exploit binary vulnerabilities and logic flaws. Using binary vulnerabilities to obtain privileges means exploiting vulnerabilities running in kernel mode to execute code, such as UAF or similar vulnerabilities in the kernel or drivers, in order to gain higher privileges."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:32
msgid "逻辑漏洞主要是利用系统的一些逻辑存在问题的机制，比如有些文件夹用户可以写入，但是会以管理员权限启动。"
msgstr "Logic flaws mainly exploit problematic mechanisms in system logic, such as folders that users can write to but that are launched with administrator privileges."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:35
msgid "任意写文件利用"
msgstr "Arbitrary File Write Exploitation"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:36
msgid "在Windows中用户可以写的敏感位置主要有以下这些"
msgstr "In Windows, sensitive locations writable by users mainly include the following:"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:38
msgid "用户自身的文件和目录，包括 ``AppData`` ``Temp``"
msgstr "The user's own files and directories, including ``AppData`` and ``Temp``"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:39
msgid "``C:\\`` ，默认情况下用户可以写入"
msgstr "``C:\\`` is writable by users by default"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:40
msgid "``C:\\ProgramData`` 的子目录，默认情况下用户可以创建文件夹、写入文件"
msgstr "Subdirectories of ``C:\\ProgramData`` allow users to create folders and write files by default"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:41
msgid "``C:\\Windows\\Temp`` 的子目录，默认情况下用户可以创建文件夹、写入文件"
msgstr "Subdirectories of ``C:\\Windows\\Temp`` allow users to create folders and write files by default"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:43
msgid "具体的ACL信息可用AccessChk, 或者PowerShell的 ``Get-Acl`` 命令查看。"
msgstr "Specific ACL information can be viewed with AccessChk or the PowerShell ``Get-Acl`` command."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:45
msgid "可以利用对这些文件夹及其子目录的写权限，写入一些可能会被加载的dll，利用dll的加载执行来获取权限。"
msgstr "Write permissions on these folders and their subdirectories can be used to place DLLs that may be loaded, and DLL loading/execution can then be used to obtain privileges."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:48
msgid "MOF"
msgstr "MOF"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:49
msgid ""
"MOF是Windows系统的一个文件（ ``c:/windows/system32/wbem/mof/nullevt.mof`` "
"）叫做\"托管对象格式\"，其作用是每隔五秒就会去监控进程创建和死亡。"
msgstr "MOF is a Windows system file (``c:/windows/system32/wbem/mof/nullevt.mof``) called \"Managed Object Format\". Its role is to monitor process creation and termination every five seconds."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:51
msgid "当拥有文件上传的权限但是没有Shell时，可以上传定制的mof文件至相应的位置，一定时间后这个mof就会被执行。"
msgstr "When file upload permission is available but no shell is present, a customized MOF file can be uploaded to the corresponding location; after a certain time, the MOF will be executed."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/privilege.rst:53
msgid "一般会采用在mof中加入一段添加管理员用户的命令的vbs脚本，当执行后就拥有了新的管理员账户。"
msgstr "A common approach is to add a VBS script containing a command that creates an administrator user to the MOF; after execution, a new administrator account is available."

